1.0.0-rc1.name: drupal/at_generator

security-coverage.message: RC releases are not covered by Drupal security advisories.

1.0.0-rc1.description: Tools for generating new sub-themes. Use this to create new themes, or clone and skin existing themes. Click "Settings" to use the generator. It is safe to uninstall this tool after you have generated your theme. Do not set this theme as default.
